description: BBQnSOMEDefinition: When cooked to perfection "Backyard BBQ" and "Old School Soul Food" clashes in your mouth creating a chemical reaction. This condition if unaddressed can often cause a individual to start an illegal Second Line on the streets of New Orleans.Our corporate mission is "Trucking to feed hungry crowds Delicious and Exciting foods that screams Affordability!"We love gourmet food, however, we choose to stick to what we know, and therefore leave the gourmet foods to the actual gourmet chefs. That being the case we created a menu that represents some of the great foods that we live to eat. Good food ain't always the healthiest. So we strive to include options that are flavorful and healthy for our customers.
name: BBQ N Some
